fields.name: Budget Tracker
fields.description: Automatically track your expenses and income using Google Sheets. Connect your bank statements and credit card data to maintain real-time budget monitoring.

client_id.label: Google OAuth Client ID
client_id.placeholder: Enter your Google OAuth Client ID
client_id.help_text: Get this from Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Credentials

client_secret.label: Google OAuth Client Secret
client_secret.placeholder: Enter your Google OAuth Client Secret
client_secret.help_text: Get this from Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Credentials

spreadsheet_id.label: Google Sheets ID
spreadsheet_id.placeholder: Enter your Google Sheets document ID
spreadsheet_id.help_text: Find this in the URL of your Google Sheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/[SPREADSHEET_ID]/edit

sheet_name.label: Sheet Name
sheet_name.help_text: Name of the sheet tab in your Google Sheets document (optional, defaults to first sheet)
